However, the two released a collaborative single for Valentine's Day, "Konclusions", on February 14, 2020.

Kehlani announced that they were pregnant with their first child, a girl, on Instagram on October 12, 2018, with the father being Javaughn Young-White, who is their guitarist.
They opened up in December 2018 about prenatal depression and how their pregnancy is harder than it might look.
On March 23, 2019, Kehlani gave birth to their daughter, Adeya Nomi Parrish Young-White at home.
